# Frontend env (Vite). Copy to ".env" only if you need to override defaults.
#
# DEV (default): leave everything unset. The app calls "/api/*" and Vite proxies
# it to the Query Service, so the browser stays same-origin and CORS never applies.
#
# If your Query Service is not on http://localhost:8080, point the dev proxy at it:
# VITE_QUERY_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:8080
#
# PRODUCTION / static hosting (no Vite proxy): call the Query Service directly.
# The browser will be cross-origin, so the service's CORS allow-list must include
# this app's origin (see backend note in README).
# VITE_QUERY_BASE=http://localhost:8080
